features: TSA Approved: TSA-approved toiletry bags strictly follow 3-1-1 regulations and 100% work internationally. All-round transparent design can help to pass through airport security quickly and save time.

High Quality: The clear toiletry bag is made of double-layer 60 Silk PVC plastic, with waterproof fabric on both sides for easy cleaning. The seams of each toiletry bag are reinforced to make the bag strong and more durable.

Durable and Sturdy: The clear makeup bag features a high-quality metal double zipper with a sturdy, wear-resistant edge that allows the toiletry bag to expand 180° horizontally for easy access and use of travel essentials, ensuring safe closure and long-term use.

Portable and Lightweight: The travel makeup bag size is 7.8*5.9*2.4 inches and weighs only 0.22 pounds, suitable for your carry-on bags or suitcases. The humanized design allows the makeup bag to be lifted and hung, making it easy to carry when traveling or on the go.

Multipurpose: The travel organizer can be used as a cosmetic bag, toiletry bag, grocery bag, toy bag, and more. You can easily place cosmetics, shampoos, toothbrushes, razors, shaving creams, facial cleansers, general medicines, etc.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 16, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Convenient and durable
reviews.reviewText: I love these bags. They come in multiple different sizes and have a nice velvet trim. The clear plastic is easy to clean and is transparent so it’s easy to see what you’re looking for. I put one of these in my purse so I can easily grab what I need. It’s also durable! My toddler has been putting all his toy cars in and out of one of the bags and the bag is still working perfectly.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 4, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Last minute purchase I am SO glad I made! Makes packing so easy!
reviews.reviewText: I was packing for a trip to Maui and trying to organize my make-up and toiletries for my carry on bag. I have a million little makeup bags from those gift with purchase deals, etc, and I have used quart zip-locks in the past. But it was just triggering my slight OCD tendencies to have stuff in non matching bags of odd sizes, and trying to separate so that liquids would be TSA ready. I found these here on Amazon and thought...do I really need them? YES! Emphatically, YES, I DO! They arrived next day. I ordered a set of three. One holds carry-on liquids and 'wet' makeup, one for 'dry' makeup and q-tips., etc, and another with face wipes, panty liners, face masks, ear plugs, etc, the stuff you want on hand that doesn't need to be pulled for the security scan. The bags have two all around zippers which is so much better than a top zipper, and you could even put a little lock on it. The square shape makes packing easier too. They hold a surprising amount of stuff! I like the handle for quick, fumble-free retrieval. They stack in my backpack perfectly. I am so happy with the quality and size and I might order more because they are just so great for packing anything in a carry on. One for snacks? One for tech cords and earbuds? And not just for travel, they could be used to organize makeup in a drawer, or for craft supplies, kids car toys...the list of possibilities is endless!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 14, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Don't let the size fool you, they hold a lot of stuff
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. These little bags hold a surprisingly amount of stuff. The zippers, clear sides, fabric all feel solid and I'm not worried about it coming apart anytime soon. I really like the handle at the top which makes it easy to carry in and out of the bathroom. The clear plastic sides and fabric are sturdy and I don't think any of my products will put a hole in them.These bags aren't completely waterproof due to the fabric siding. The outside fabric is a suede like fabric and the inside fabric feels similar to the inside of a lunchbox (aka fabric that can take a beating).The 2 zippers haven't snagged and work well on all three bags. I love that there they are sold as three high quality bags in one package. I'm actually excited to use these when traveling!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 10, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great quality clear bag for travel
reviews.reviewText: This is a perfect quart sized bag that should be tsa approved for my carry on. It has a handle, which is nice for quick and easy access!

These are the perfect size that I was searching for, for a 2-night getaway! Not too big, not too small. Big enough to hold a full-size toothbrush, and more-importantly, the zippers go all the way around 3 sides, so it opens fully like a suitcase. Most other toiletry bags open like an envelope, making it impossible lay the bag flat & access everything easily. Love the clear panels (essential) and like that the sides are cloth instead of plastic.
